al elementor-global-4670 elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"e5c01f6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-lg\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/appointment\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Book An Appointment<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8665deb\" data-id=\"8665deb\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-2ae8172 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2ae8172\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8a014d3\" data-id=\"8a014d3\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6dcd759 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6dcd759\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Preventing Weevil Infestations<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ce426c5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ce426c5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Weevils can easily find their way into your home through cracks in walls or floors. The first step in preventing weevil infestations is to ensure that all food items are properly sealed in airtight containers. This includes flour, cereal, rice, pasta, and any other dry goods.<\/p><p>Another effective method for preventing weevils is to freeze your dry goods before storing them. Freezing kills any eggs or larvae that may be present in the product before it&#8217;s stored. If you notice any signs of weevils or other pests, such as small holes or web-like material around your stored food items, it&#8217;s best to dispose of them immediately.<\/p><p>Lastly, keeping your home clean and clutter-free can also help prevent weevil infestations. Regularly vacuuming floors and wiping down surfaces where crumbs may accumulate will reduce the likelihood of attracting these pests into your home. By following these simple tips, you can help prevent weevils from damaging your stored foods and keep them out of your home.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Weevils Identification Color Size Description Color Some Weevils are brightly colored with intricate patterns, while others are plain black or brown. Size Weevils come in various sizes, with some species measuring just a few millimeters in length while others can reach up to 6 mm. Description Weevils are generally small and have a characteristic snout &#8230; <a title=\"Weevils\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/acmepestsolutions.com\/weevils\/\" aria-label=\"More on Weevils\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6686,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template